data.eml:eml: Chronicle of Nature - Phenology of Reptiles of Kondinskie Lakes National Park named after L. F. Stashkevich

Reptiles Phenology dataset compiled in the context of Chronicle of Nature program in Kondinskie Lakes National Park named after L. F. Stashkevich (Russian Federation) consisting of 14 records collected during 8 years between 2001 and 2008.
